# Website to llms.txt

- **Route**: `GET /llms.txt?url=<url>` (url required, http/https only).
- **Response**: `Content-Type: text/plain`; body is llms.txt-style (title, description, Key Information links, Contact).
- **Bindings**: None.
- **Utils**: `validateUrl`, fetch + HTML parse; error shape `{ error, code }` for 400/502.
